snippet: Eight men were charged with trafficking in high-caliber weapons that included a cannon.
abstract: Eight members of three Brooklyn-based motorcycle gangs are arrested and charged with trafficking high-caliber weapons; defendants, ranging in age from 33 to 61, face up to five years in prison if convicted.
lead_paragraph: Eight men were charged with trafficking in high-caliber weapons that included a cannon.

headline.seo: Motorcycle Gang Members Arrested on Weapons Trafficking Charge
headline.main: Members of Brooklyn Motorcycle Gangs Arrested on Weapons Charges
headline.print_headline: Gang Members Are Charged With Dealing In Weapons
